case.title: seeking for man who is ready for serious relationship - 33 (Anywhere in Europe)
case.text: Im a decent, loving, honest woman who is looking for the same in a man. I have a great sense of humor and like to laugh.Am divorce with one daughter and love to spoil other peoples. I can have anymore if you really want, but I dont do drugs and drink occasionally. I believe that trust and communication are the keys to a successful relationship. If you feel the same way respond to this ad and we'll go from there.
